summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the improvement of Roosevelt Way Northeast from Northeast 92nd Street to Pinehurst Way Northeast and a certain other street and avenue, by constructing concrete sidewalks, etc., and otherwise improving the same, Local Improvement District No. 6357, appropriating additional funds from the City Street Fund; authorizing additional funds from the Water Fund, and amending Section 1 of Ordinance No. 96516, and Section 2 of Ordinance No. 96515.
